title: The Empire Strikes Back (1980 Original Version)
description:
This is the original 1980 version. Source is DVD presented in a letterbox format for old 4:3 televisions. That has been corrected.

After the rebels have been brutally overpowered by the Empire on their newly-established base, Luke Skywalker takes advanced Jedi training with Yoda, while his friends are constantly being pursued by Vader as part of his plan to capture Luke. Rated PG
